{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_07_01_short",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 恋する少女、一ノ瀬怜 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私をヒロインにした恋愛ゲーム……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Making me the heroine of a romance game…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ。ゲーム会社の持ち込み企画で、星見プロの\nアイドルを使ったゲームを作ることになったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that's right. It's a project brought in by a game company\nto create a game featuring Hoshimi Prods.'s idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私がヒロインだなんていいんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But is it really okay for me to be the heroine?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ヒロインはあくまで『一ノ瀬怜』という\nキャラクターだから、そんなに気負わなくて大丈夫だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The heroine is just the character \"Rei Ichinose‚\"\nso don't worry too much about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれませんが、自分がゲームに出ると思うと\nやっぱり恥ずかしいし、緊張します……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That may be true‚ but I still feel embarrassed and\nnervous thinking about appearing in a game…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "私と疑似恋愛するゲームなんて\n楽しんでもらえるんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will people really enjoy a game where\nthey pretend to have a romance with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーム会社の人達は「ぜひ怜で」と言っているし\nファンも怜の新しい一面を見られて嬉しいと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The people at the game company are insisting on starring Rei‚\nand I think fans will be happy to see a new side of Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね。分かりました\nそれで私は具体的に何をすればいいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see. Understood.\nSo what specifically should I do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}